main_body:
The Belgian Government is hereby authorized to grant aid totalling Bfr 1 696 180 000 to the Belgian coal industry for the 1992 calendar year. The total amount shall be made up of the following aid:
1. aid to cover operating losses not exceeding Bfr 1 386 980 000;
2. aid to finance social benefit schemes in the coal industry not exceeding Bfr 299 200 000;
3. aid to cover expenses relating to the systems of supplementary holiday for underground workers, not exceeding Bfr 10 000 000.
